steps.name: Given I am on the "Welcome" page
Given I click on the "Enter The Store Link"
Given I am on the "Catalog" page
When I click on the "Dogs" in the sidebar section
Then I am on the "Category" page
When I click on the product "K9-BD-01"
Then I am on the "Product" page
When I click on the item link for item ID "EST-7"
Then I am on the "Item" page
When I click on the "Add To Cart Button"
Then I am on the "Cart" page
And The page title "JPetStore Demo" and the URL "https://petstore.octoperf.com/actions/Cart.action?addItemToCart=&workingItemId=EST-7" should match the expected value
